node.text:
A lot of shooters have a hard time figuring out how to load the hips while moving and shooting. We see the hips sink forward in front of the shoulders, which takes away from our mobility and how explosive we can be. Simple little trick to find what right is in the video. 
__________

VC: @berserkercreative 
__________

@viktosbrand #viktoslife #shooter #tee #operatus #pant @official_staccato2011 #staccato @leupoldoptics #leupold #moving #getshooty #baersolutions #dte #zedo

node.text: I don’t get political on here, there’s enough of that already. This is a speech that I think everyone, despite political beliefs, should listen too. Proud to say Rep. Dan Crenshaw is from my hometown of Houston, TX.

node.title: Rep. Crenshaw, The Miracle of America

node.text:
Talking about cognitive stress, story my good buddy tells back at my old unit, and how to solve problems. Discussion post barrier stress shoot with LE and Mil students at Prado Olympic Shooting Park in Los Angeles.
@viktosbrand @spiritussystems #viktoslife #police #training #california

BAER-15 Rifle is now available and live on @tacticaledgeusa website. If you are on the BAER email list, we just sent out an email with links. 
・・・
B A E R ▫️ S O L U T I O N S⁠
⁠
Available now in a limited run of 20, will ship within 48 hours. These will go fast!⁠
⁠
Drew Estell is an Army Special Forces veteran who specialized in Military Free-Fall Operations and completed 7 deployments fighting the war on terror. During his time spent in the Middle East, he conducted direct action missions against high-value targets, trained foreign special operation forces, and conducted Village Stability Operations. This is his rifle.⁠
⁠
